---
layout: layouts/page.njk
---
{% block body %}
  <div class="hero">
    <h1 class="h1 text-center text-secondary font-sans font-bold py-4">
      Continuous and on-demand <br/>monitoring and auditing
    </h1>
    <h2 class="h2 text-center mx-0 lg:mx-44 py-4">
      Take your website to the next level
    </h2>
  </div>

  <section class="card hover:shadow-lg">
    <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-4">
      <div>
        {% image "img/monthly-weekly-monitoring.png", "Sitefig dashboard" %}

      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-left">Regular website monitoring and auditing is the key to success.</h4>

        <p>
          Sitefig regularly checks your website's performance, and functionality to identify potential issue and so you
          don't have to waste time.
          This allows you to stay on top of any issues and make necessary updates in a timely manner
        </p>
        <p>Website monitoring and auditing should be done on a regular basis, ideally at least once a month.</p>

        <p>By regularly monitoring and auditing your website, you can ensure that it is functioning at
          its best, is accessible to all users, and is free from errors and compliance issues. </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container md:max-w-2xl mx-auto flex flex-wrap justify-center py-8">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal to-cyan p-6 rounded text-black text-center ">
      <a class="h4 block" href="https://app.sitefig.eu/accounts/signup/">
        Try out sitefig for free, and set up a DEMO account.<br/>
        <small>(Scan 100 pages for free)</small>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="card hover:shadow-lg">
    <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-4">
      <div>
        {% image "img/cookies-gdpr.png", "A screenshot of the cookies dashboard with navigation providing access to Cookies, Trackers and much more" %}
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-left">Get compliant, stay compliant</h4>
        <p>In today's digital age, having a website is not only a necessity for most businesses, but it also comes with
          legal responsibilities.
        <p>
        <p>Regular website monitoring and auditing can help you stay compliant with industry
          regulations and best practices.</p>
        <p>Sitefig checks the cookies and trackers on your website for to make sure that your DPO stays on top of
          privacy issues.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div
    class="text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan to-teal rounded shadow mt-10 mb-10 lg:mx-64 p-6 font-sans font-bold">
    <figure role="group">
      <img src="/img/mozilla-matjas.jpg" class="max-h-32 inline rounded-full"/>
      <blockquote class="text-white">
        Sitefig is so far ahead in terms of error detection.
      </blockquote>
      <figcaption>
        <span class="text-white">Matjas Horvat</span>
        <cite class="text-white text-sm">
          <a href="https://www.mozilla.si/author/matjaz-horvat/">
            Software engineer at moz://a - Mozilla
          </a>
        </cite>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>


  </div>

  <section class="card hover:shadow-lg">
    <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-4">
      <div>
        {% image "img/privacy-statement.png", "The privacy statement as an example for why DPOs collect cookies lists" %}
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-left">Tired of asking the list of cookies?</h4>
        <p>Despite your DPOs repeated requests, the IT and development teams oftens struggles to provide DPOs with the
          information they need. </p>
        <p>IT is usually too busy with their own projects to take the time to gather the details,
          and when they do provide the information, it is often incomplete, inaccurate or already outdated.
        </p>
        <p>With Sitefig, Any DPO can log in an get all the necessary data from the dashboard, or download to a
          spreadsheet.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endblock %}
